title: Chet Atkins - Solo Sessions
description:
Solo Sessions is a posthumous release of solo guitar recordings by Chet Atkins. All the songs are previously unreleased and were recorded by Chet in his home studio. Chet's grandson Jonathan, longtime sideman Paul Yandell and engineer Mike Poston undertook the task of cataloging, organizing and releasing this two-CD set. Some of the songs were unique and new versions of previously released songs.
